TITLE
Misbegotten Part 3
PREVIOUSLY ON STARGATE ATLANTIS
[Scenes from SGA 2.20 "Allies Part 1" and SGA 3.01 "No Man's Land Part
2" are shown.]
EXT--CHEYENNE MOUNTAIN, DAY
INT--SGC CONTROL ROOM
[Weir waits anxiously in the busy control room.]
HARRIMAN
(over intercom)
Incoming wormhole.
(to Weir)
Opening the iris. Receiving video transmission.
[Teyla appears on a monitor.]
TEYLA
(over transmission)
Stargate Command, this is Atlantis.
WEIR
I'm here, Teyla. Any word about our people?
TEYLA
(over comm)
Unfortunately...no. But the hive ship we have been tracking is still
