[Weir nods.]
WEIR
Written by...?
WOOLSEY
(shrugs reluctantly)
Me. I'll be going back to Atlantis with you.
WEIR
Have you ever been offworld before, Mister Woolsey?
WOOLSEY
Sure. Once.
WEIR
And how did that go for you?
WOOLSEY
I was nearly killed.
WEIR
Well, we will do our best to make sure that doesn't happen...this
