[Lathan pauses outside a tent, then enters.]
INT--TENT
[Lathan joins several human-Wraith sitting in the tent. They appear to
be waiting for him.]
MERRICK
What did he say?
LATHAN
Nothing. He won't tell us anything. He's hiding something.
