EXT--SOUTH RIDGE, DAY
[Beckett climbs to the area where Lathan was found.]
MORRISON
(over radio)
Doctor Beckett, this is Lieutenant Morrison. What's your location?
BECKETT
(into radio)
I'm out on the ridge where Lathan's body was found.
